&lt;p>간단한 인공 신경망 모델 만들기 &lt;a href="https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/cs/cs12/#17-%ea%b0%84%eb%8b%a8%ed%95%9c-%ec%9d%b8%ea%b3%b5-%ec%8b%a0%ea%b2%bd%eb%a7%9d-%eb%aa%a8%eb%8d%b8-%eb%a7%8c%eb%93%a4%ea%b8%b0">&amp;raquo;&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
