&lt;p>인공 신경망에 층을 추가하여 심층 신경망 만들어 보기 &lt;a href="https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/cs/cs12/#18-%ec%9d%b8%ea%b3%b5-%ec%8b%a0%ea%b2%bd%eb%a7%9d%ec%97%90-%ec%b8%b5%ec%9d%84-%ec%b6%94%ea%b0%80%ed%95%98%ec%97%ac-%ec%8b%ac%ec%b8%b5-%ec%8b%a0%ea%b2%bd%eb%a7%9d-%eb%a7%8c%eb%93%a4%ea%b8%b0">&amp;raquo;&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
